              "free_text": [
                "The error in the deuteron energy scale was",
                "estimated to be between 0.5 and 0.7 MeV.",
                "The error on cross sections is estimated by combining",
                "the contributing sources in quadrature:",
                "    Beam current               12%",
                "    Number of target nuclei     3%",
                "    Decay data                  2%",
                "    Detector efficiency was     5%",
                "    Statisztical error          3%",
                "    Peak Area Determination     3%",
                "    Decay curve analysis error  5% for 13N, and 11C",
                "    Decay curve analysis error  5-15% for 15O Ed<7MeV",
                "    Decay curve analysis error  25% for 15O Ed>7MeV",
                " Total error for 13N and 11C is about 15%, for 15O",
                " is about 20% below 7 MeV and about 30% above 7 MeV."
              ]
